UAE Board::Public Relations Officer (PRO)
Public Relations Officer (PRO) Human Resource
SCHOOL ADMINISTRATION POST. SSAT (Middle East) is a well-respected Consultancy, working with a large educational foundation to open a new school in Mohammed Bin Zayed City, to start in September 2014. We are seeking staff members to start work with us from early May. Applicants should send their CV, a photograph, current salary, and the names and contact details of 2 referees to: hr2@ssat.me by Monday, 5th May. State the position you are applying for in the subject line of your email. Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted, and responses will be made as CVs are received. SSAT Website: www.ssat.me | The language used in the administration will be English.Public Relations Officer (PRO) - This position will be based in the Human Resource Department to undertake the official submission of documentation to government departments. Excellent knowledge of the UAE labor law, experience of working with government departments as a PRO and bilingual (Arabic / English) is a requirement. Immediate start.Applicants should send their CV, a photograph, current salary, and the names and contact details of 2 referees to: hr2@ssat.me by Monday, 5th May. State the position you are applying for in the subject line of your email. Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted, and responses will be made as CVs are received. SSAT Website: www.ssat.me
